{"tid":874741,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"中國連續7屆無緣世青盃","createTime":"2018-10-24T12:04:46.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-26T12:49:57.000Z","uid":109743,"like":22,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"074ef87b98e97f6bc852cffd52ba68f85285e5e2","tid":874741,"uid":109743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T12:04:46.000Z","msg":"U19亞洲盃小組賽第二輪，馬來西亞U19與塔吉克U19戰成2比2，這也意味著中國U19提前出局，同時無緣明年的世青盃。<br />\n<br />\n小組賽前兩輪，中國U19分別以0比1的比分輸給塔吉克U19和沙地阿拉伯U19。兩輪過後，沙地阿拉伯U19積6分提前出線，塔吉克U19積4分，馬來西亞U19積1分，中國U19則以0分墊底，提前出局。<br />\n<br />\n這也意味著中國U19將無緣明年的世青盃，本次U19亞洲盃四強才能拿到明年世青盃的參賽資格。自2005年之後，中國U19連續7屆世青盃都沒能取得參賽資格。"},{"pid":"b9618c0d0fb1385a11ed257a7ed1e2a0d49a5409","tid":874741,"uid":109743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T15:23:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e440e4f4a68fa3bd8a6d89bd3536c37069d3315","tid":874741,"uid":67225,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T15:42:04.000Z","msg":"咁都算新聞？"},{"pid":"14e109d4f26d414e1bcd027782c4d2670fd98584","tid":874741,"uid":109743,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"4e440e4f4a68fa3bd8a6d89bd3536c37069d3315","tid":874741,"uid":67225,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T15:42:04.000Z","msg":"咁都算新聞？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T10:06:14.000Z","msg":"連續70屆都唔係新聞"},{"pid":"2fcad0c0aece9fb77727d88e90c65b1470f0a485","tid":874741,"uid":58174,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T10:10:36.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/L4BuQPkLSTs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FL4BuQPkLSTs&d=TfZYDYXcrxxb4%2B8FkDEgtv9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=585ce6a5\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/L4BuQPkLSTs</a>"},{"pid":"f6249c09bfa306c2e7172619fec979ed3a737359","tid":874741,"uid":146833,